articles.content: Employees of shops nearby told the Chinese daily they were not sure what happened. The police said that they received a call for assistance at around 5.50am. Officers found the deceased motionless. He was pronounced dead on the spot by a Singapore Civil Defence Force paramedic. Based on preliminary investigations, the police do not suspect foul play.
